OL,3,CBin strike: plenty of promises, but no
OL,4,Cparty has a clear way out
OL,6,FPolling suggests ending Birmingham's
OL,7,Flong-running bin strike is the top
OL,8,Fpriority for voters.
OL,10,FEvery party says it wants a
OL,11,Fresolution. Every party talks about
OL,12,Fnegotiations.
OL,14,FBut when pressed on the central
OL,15,Fobstacle to a deal, none offer a clear
OL,16,Fpath through it.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
