PN,37214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776863483
OL,3,CBin strike: plenty of promises, but no
OL,4,Cparty has a clear way out
OL,6,FWithout a way through the legal
OL,7,Fdeadlock, any new administration would
OL,8,Fface the same constraints.
OL,10,FFor now, no party has shown how it
OL,11,Fwould break the cycle.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/14
